user.biography:
Discover the world with us!
Founded by @coskunenes.

node.text:
Lifting each other up now and always! ❤️ Cinthia Zanuni writes, “Choose for your life someone who has the power to make you feel like you're floating. Choose someone who will make you climb steps in life even if you can't walk on your own legs. Choose someone who decides every day to thank you even if they have reasons to complain.”
Tag a friend who is there for you!

Credits: @cinthiazanuni & @hugoecinthia.

node.text:
🇮🇷 Rainbow Island, Iran.
The soil composing Hormuz Island in #Iran is highly concentrated with Iron Oxide. This concentration leads to red coloration, which is washed up in the waves.
Have you ever seen anything like this?

Credits: @elhamgholami.
